

An health assistant that provides personalized health advice and tracks health-related data. This program is built using Python and includes a graphical user interface (GUI) for easy interaction.
[THIS IS FOR SAMPLE PURPOSES ONLY, THIS DOES NOT REPLACE A TRAINED MEDICAL PROFESSIONAL!!!!]

## Features

- Get personalized health advice from the AI Health Assistant.
- Track your daily steps and get feedback on your progress.

## Requirements

- Python 3.7 or higher
- tkinter (already included with most Python installations)

## Installation

1. Clone this repository to your local machine:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-health-assistant.git
```

2. Change into the project directory:

```bash
cd ai-health-assistant
```

3. Run the AI Health Assistant program:

```bash
python main.py
```

## How to Use

1. Launch the AI Health Assistant program by running source code
2. The GUI will open, displaying a health advice text and an input field for daily steps.
3. Read the health advice displayed on the GUI.
4. Input your daily steps in the provided input field.
5. Click on the "Track Steps" button to track your daily steps. You will receive feedback on the number of steps tracked.

## Note

This AI Health Assistant currently provides random health advice for demonstration purposes. For real-world use, you would need to integrate more sophisticated AI models and health data APIs to provide personalized advice.

